      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">12.504</ph> Applicability of certain	laws to subcontracts for the acquisition of commercial items.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d712e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d739e10" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
						            The following laws are not applicable	to subcontracts at any tier for the acquisition of commercial items	or commercial components at any tier:</p>
