                              format="html"
                              scope="external"
                              class="- topic/xref ">10 U.S.C.2631</xref>, Transportation	of Supplies by Sea (except for the types of subcontracts listed	at <xref href="47.504.dita#FAR_47_504"
                              base="i1069858"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">47.504</xref>(d)).</p>
                  </li>
