                              format="html"
                              scope="external"
                              class="- topic/xref ">15 U.S.C.644(d)</xref>, Requirements	relative to labor surplus areas under the Small Business Act (see <xref href="Subpart_19.2.dita#FAR_Subpart_19_2"
                              base="i1101515"
                              outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                              class="- topic/xref ">subpart  19.2</xref>).</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d739e36" class="- topic/p ">
