            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d739e152" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
						            The requirements	for a certificate and clause under the Contract Work Hours and Safety	Standards statute, <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">40 U.S.C.37</xref>, (see <xref href="Subpart_22.3.dita#FAR_Subpart_22_3"
                        base="i1098304"
                        outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                        class="- topic/xref ">subpart  22.3</xref>) are	not applicable to subcontracts at any tier for the acquisition of	commercial items or commercial components.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d739e163" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
						            The applicability	of the following laws has been modified in regards to subcontracts	at any tier for the acquisition of commercial items or commercial	components:</p>
               <ol id="d712e250" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d739e169" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                              format="html"
                              scope="external"
                              class="- topic/xref ">41 U.S.C.4704</xref> and <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                              format="html"
                              scope="external"
                              class="- topic/xref ">10 U.S.C.2402</xref>, Prohibition	on Limiting Subcontractor Direct Sales to the United States (see <xref href="Subpart_3.5.dita#FAR_Subpart_3_5"
                              base="i1124321"
                              outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                              class="- topic/xref ">subpart  3.5</xref>).</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d739e182" class="- topic/p ">
